<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#6a663fdbb8694a8ea8d141c:InPrivacyPolicy">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#InPrivacyPolicy"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">6a663fdbb8694a8ea8d141c</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Important Update In September 2012 we announced that Instagram had been acquired by Facebook We knew that by teaming up with Facebook we could build a better Instagram for you Since then we ve been collaborating with Facebook s team on ways to do just that As part of our new collaboration we ve learned that by being able to share insights and information with each other we can build better experiences for our users</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

